data: not unified with U+082B2, irg49. pending for solusions (not unified by U+082B2, G source of U+082B2 may be changed), irg47. unified by U+082B2, irg46.
This character is the simplified form of U+83D5 菕 lún "a type of plant", and is not cognate with U+82B2 芲 (a variant form of U+82B1 花 huā "flower").
